{"tid":401654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無線新聞 別有用心】美警擊斃持刀及假槍男子 當局指勸喻不果後開槍","createTime":"2017-09-15T19:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T04:52:34.000Z","uid":88743,"like":75,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b723cf9ce03926336c3fe683dc048d4320f78e1","tid":401654,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T19:04:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/59bb62dee60383d9216c90cd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F59bb62dee60383d9216c90cd%2F&d=nwSJY%2FbG28RFYiZiWQlr5v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c172e0a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/59bb62dee60383d9216c90cd/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國紐約警方開始配備隨身攝錄機後，首次拍下警員開槍擊斃可疑人士片段。警員連開十六槍，擊斃一名持刀及懷疑槍械男子，事後證實男子所持的為假槍。當局強調，警員是在多番勸喻不果後才開槍。<br />\n<br />\n警察勸喻：「給我看看你的手、給我看看你的手。」<br />\n<br />\n事發於上星期三，紐約兩名警員首先到場，失蹤多時、被房東報警尋人，31歲租客理查茲站在睡房一角。他一手持刀，另一手則藏著。<br />\n<br />\n警察稱：「我不想向你開槍，舉高手，把刀放下。」<br />\n<br />\n隨後理查茲友人趕到，加入遊說行列，多次呼籲他放下刀。理查茲友人說：「小子，把刀放下吧，拜託你，我不願見到你受傷，就把刀放下吧。」<br />\n<br />\n警員之後發現，理查茲另一隻手拿著疑似槍枝，立即命令他放下。<br />\n<br />\n警員說：「理查茲，你拿著的是真槍嗎？理查茲，我不想開槍，若你手持的是假槍，聽到嗎？如果是真槍的話，我會開槍，把槍拋到地上，放下刀，聽到嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">理查茲全程不發一言，警方指當時他手持之物，發出如瞄準目標的紅色鐳射光束，同一時間第三名警員趕到，持電擊槍進入睡房。<br />\n<br />\n理查茲衝前，最先到場的兩名警員隨即開火，分別開了九槍和七槍，理查茲當場被擊斃，當局事後證實他手持的是假槍。</span>今次是紐約警方四月起，陸續配備隨身攝錄機後，首次拍得警員擊斃可疑人士。<br />\n<br />\n當局將全方位徹查事件，但強調警員曾多番勸喻，包括四十四次喝令對方放下刀、六次要求拋掉槍枝不果後才開槍，死者父親則批評兒子被冷血殺害。<br />\n<br />\n因應近年美國警方執勤時多番被指濫用暴力，紐約市長白思豪年初與工會達成協議，全市二萬多名巡警，於2019年將全面配備隨身攝錄機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n我睇完呢單新聞, 心諗 下 美國咁撚ON9 po自己友無理隊死持刀假槍男子出黎俾人屌? 唔會掛<br />\n之後搵返美國既報紙, 屌你老味TVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/14/nyregion/police-body-camera-footage-new-york.html?mcubz=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2Fnyregion%2Fpolice-body-camera-footage-new-york.html%3Fmcubz%3D0&d=nwSJY%2FbG28RFYiZiWQlr5v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c4e5e83a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2017/09/14/nyregion/police-body-camera-footage-new-york.html?mcubz=0</a><br />\n<br />\n「Put it down.」<br />\n<br />\n「This isn't going to end well.」<br />\n<br />\n「What's in your other hand? You don't understand &mdash; you're seconds away from getting shot if you don't tell us what's in your other hand.」<br />\n<br />\n「Do you want to die?」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">After about 15 minutes, an officer with a Taser stun gun steps through the doorway to try to use the weapon to shock and subdue Mr. Richards. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>At that moment, Mr. Richards raises his arm &mdash; the one in which the officers had earlier observed what appeared to be a gun.</strong></ins></span> In an instant, the officer with the Taser fires the stun gun as two officers behind him fire their service weapons, killing Mr. Richards in a hail of 16 bullets. The object in his hand turned out to be a toy gun.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粗體字係警察連開十幾槍既原因 人地nytimes條片最後仲要慢鏡影埋條友真係舉起支laser槍<br />\n屌你老味無線一隻字都無撚提過佢舉起支槍 條片仲要CUT撚埋<br />\n唔好咁撚狗咁撚低莊以為無人知啦濕鳩無線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im